Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:31.94,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:37.50,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,Smoking's not allowed\N on school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:42.44,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,Clubs don't meet \Nduring exam period, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:46.67,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,I run every day \Nso I don't get out of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:50.50,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,Wow. And what do you do \Nfor strength training?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:53.24,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,I just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:56.70,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,Really? And you're that jacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:57.26,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:00:58.20,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.83,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,You just run?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:03.46,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,I just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:05.46,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,You run?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:07.15,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:11.89,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go for a run, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:14.47,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,You can't smoke off \Nschool grounds, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:58.57,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fnComic Sans MS\b1\blur0.3\bord0.5\fs30\shad2\pos(462,315)\3c&H0E0E0E&\4c&H0E0E0E&}A New Discovery!\NA Study Session After School!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:58.57,Top,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,Double-check your work \Nif you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.88,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,Okay, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.45,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,Turn your tests in from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:10.82,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,There's only one more day of exams, \Nbut don't relax just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:14.84,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,I worked {\i1}real{\i0} hard \Non tomorrow's math test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:14.84,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\an1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fnArial\b1\fs20\c&HB8B5AB&\pos(20,58)}1st Period: English
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:14.84,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\an1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fnArial\b1\fs20\c&HB8B5AB&\pos(20,128)}2nd Period:\NJapanese History
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:14.84,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\an1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fnArial\b1\fs20\c&HB8B5AB&\pos(20,268)}3rd Period:\NPhysics
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:18.05,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Huh? Dude, I just can't with math.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.75,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I suck at math.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:25.81,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Man, I'm beat. Guess I'll go\N study in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.44,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)\fnArial\fscx80\bord2.5\b1\shad0\fs14\blur0.3\c&H454353&\3c&HF2EEF0&\pos(177.5,128)}Borrow up to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.44,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)\fnArial\fscx80\bord2.5\b1\shad0\fs14\blur0.3\c&H454353&\3c&HF2EEF0&\pos(177.5,161)}2 books for 2 weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.82,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I knew it'd be crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:37.51,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,There aren't any open tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.48,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Guess I'll study at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.74,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Nakamura. Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.29,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,H-Hirose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.45,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.33,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,N-Next to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.04,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I'll be sitting next to Hirose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.58,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Really? Is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.58,Flashback Top,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.42,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.84,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,You studying for exams, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.22,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.75,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,He's too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:01.22,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Yeah. He came crying to me \Nand asked to see my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:03.60,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.17,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,It's not like taking notes now will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:09.23,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, it's just a stopgap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.58,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:14.98,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Huh? A-A stopgap. \NA last-minute temporary fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.33,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,I've never heard that word before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.74,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,If you're good at modern Japanese, \Nmaybe you can teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.97,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,What? U-Uh, sure. If you're okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.37,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Thanks, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.50,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Am I going to die tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.00,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fscx80\bord2.5\b1\shad0\fs14\blur0.3\c&H454353&\3c&HF2EEF0&\pos(177.5,128)}Borrow up to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.00,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fscx80\bord2.5\b1\shad0\fs14\blur0.3\c&H454353&\3c&HF2EEF0&\pos(177.5,161)}2 books for 2 weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.05,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Th-This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:36.71,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I'm too distracted by Hirose to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.40,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.26,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,"Ha"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.55,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Ha... "Hakaana"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.22,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,To dig a grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.55,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(365,45)\fnGeorgia\b1\fax-0.155\fay-0.02\fscy90\fscx90\bord0\shad0\c&H00030E&\frz341.3\frx10}5\h\h{\fs20}Dig a grave (Hakaana)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.55,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnGeorgia\b1\fax-0.125\fscy20\fscx25\bord1\1a&HFF&\shad0\c&H00030E&\frz341.5\frx20\p1\pos(357.5,45)}m 50 0 b 100 0 100 100 50 100 b 0 100 0 0 50 0{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.85,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,He's so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:48.06,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,What's next? Ah, "kinsen."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.06,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(365,46)\fnGeorgia\b1\fax-0.225\fay-0.02\fscy90\fscx90\bord0\shad0\c&H00030E&\frz341.3\frx10}6\h\h{\fs20}Touch heartstrings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.06,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnGeorgia\b1\fax-0.125\fscy20\fscx25\bord1\1a&HFF&\shad0\c&H00030E&\frz341.5\frx20\p1\pos(358.5,42.5)}m 50 0 b 100 0 100 100 50 100 b 0 100 0 0 50 0{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.09,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.06,Default,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,"Ko"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.44,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnComic Sans MS\bord0\fs60\shad0\b1\c&H7A3DD8&\pos(18.5,215)}Kotose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.44,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnComic Sans MS\bord0\fs60\shad0\b1\c&H7A3DD8&\t(1000,1400,\frz-55)\move(153.5,213.5,148,204,1000,1400)}n
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.36,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Kotosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.94,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,No, stop. Focus on studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.97,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Hey, are you guys hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.64,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,I'm too hungry to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.71,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess. We haven't had lunch yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:04.77,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Wanna get some bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.33,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Isn't the school store closed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:10.68,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Aw, what? But I'm starving to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.08,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Should we go to \Nthat new family restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.03,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Great idea! Let's go there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:17.80,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Sounds good. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.70,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.08,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,They're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.86,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.81,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Let's go, Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:33.83,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.32,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnVerdana\b1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs15\c&HBDE6FA&\move(522,142,507,142)}Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.20,Top,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Man, I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.26,Top,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Now that I've eaten, I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.57,Top,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:43.29,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Th-This is my first time coming to \Nthis kind of restaurant without my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.57,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I was so nervous, \NI couldn't taste my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.85,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Did you see yesterday's \N{\i1}Detective Bari Kata{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.67,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:51.83,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Did you see it, Hirose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.71,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,From the side. My family watched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:56.39,Top,MUKAI,0,0,0,,The protagonist is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.94,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Huh? What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.46,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,I only care about the female lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.59,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Do you watch that show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.83,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Uh, a little of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:06.29,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,My sister's really into it.\N It's super popular right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.11,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.72,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,I like that actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.98,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Yeah, I bet you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.56,Top,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Yeah, she looks like Hamaoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.98,Top,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,No, she doesn't. \NYuuka-chan is way cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:16.57,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Crap! I have no clue what it is!\N I'll look it up later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:17.98,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Scribble, scribble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.75,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Oh, nice. I like this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.86,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.18,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,It's all you listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.43,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:30.32,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Didn't you borrow their album \Nfrom Ohmori the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.75,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.88,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,We're going to a concert soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.39,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.97,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Wait. With Ohmori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:41.88,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous! I want to go \Nto a concert with just Hirose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.61,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Nakamura, do you have any favorite music?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:48.01,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Uh, I-I listen to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.80,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.99,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,When I'm into something, \Nit's all I listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:56.17,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,I'm into this band called Aquapet. \NDo you know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.26,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:00.13,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Whoa! There's a {\i1}SmaFi{\i0} update!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:02.01,Top,HIROSE,0,0,0,,What? Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.03,Top,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,What's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:04.03,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,C'mon! Can't I come up \Nwith anything better than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.54,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,There's a bunch of new levels!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:09.16,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Oh, dang. We should play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:12.16,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Let's meet at Yoshida's place \Nwhen exams are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.59,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,I can't wait. Let's play now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.45,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,I know the exams are easy \Nfor you, but screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.35,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,You're the only one who's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.88,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Hey, should we wager something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:21.65,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,On the exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:22.27,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.30,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.84,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smash Fighter{\i0}. It's really big right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.22,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:33.47,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I do. It's popular, right?\NThough I actually haven't played it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.61,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Really? It's fun. You should try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.52,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I lied. I just learned about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.40,Top,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}SmaFi{\i0} popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:38.55,Top,MUKAI,0,0,0,,This is a starter level. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.23,Top,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,I love this weapons update.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.20,Top,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Huh? What's your current rating?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:44.95,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,{\i0}Smash Fighter{\i1}, was it? \NI'll look it up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.61,Top,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Around 70?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.95,Top,MUKAI,0,0,0,,You'll get one-shotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.72,Top,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Nah, don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.11,Top,MUKAI,0,0,0,,I'm all out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.36,Top,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,What? You play too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.52,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,I'm getting a drink. \NWant anything, Nakamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.12,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Oh, u-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.29,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,I'll take a cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.50,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Ginger ale for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.87,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Seriously, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.75,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:06.26,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.47,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Oh, it's okay. It'd be hard \Nto carry four cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.39,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,There's that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.64,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,But I thought maybe you wanted \Nto study quietly by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.14,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.01,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Oh, no. No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:23.94,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,What am I doing? \NI'm making Hirose worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:30.91,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,And I still don't know anything\N about Hirose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.90,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Nakamura, you like coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:42.54,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Uh, y-yeah. I guess I drink a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.55,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Huh. It's not really my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.94,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Oh, but I like café au lait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.80,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that's good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:55.07,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Hirose can't drink black coffee? \NThat tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:58.34,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Oh, my sister says it's good \Nwith hot chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:01.56,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,R-Really? Maybe I'll try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:07.46,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Well? Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.22,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.83,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll try it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.60,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think you could drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.71,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,I'm putting something in my drink, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.09,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I didn't know about this, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:26.73,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,I know. Let's put coffee \Nin Takeuchi's cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:27.46,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.19,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Don't tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.52,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Hirose likes to pull pranks, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.73,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:37.93,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.17,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.73,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.42,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:45.01,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Shut up. Get your own drink, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.23,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\u1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs12\t(\fs13)\b1\an1\c&H45444A&\frz22.88\move(212,64,205,54)}Detective Bari Kata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs12\t(\fs13)\b1\an1\c&H45444A&\frz22.88\move(205.5,89,197.5,81)}Watches with family
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\u1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs12\t(\fs13)\b1\an1\c&H45444A&\frz22.88\move(191.5,114.5,182.5,108.5)}TV show
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs12\t(\fs13)\b1\an9\c&H45444A&\frz22.88\move(304.5,51,304.5,40)}Sister is really\Ninto it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs10\t(\fs11)\b1\an1\c&H45444A&\move(172.5,165,160.5,165)\frz23.22}Currently popular
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\u1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs12\t(\fs13)\b1\an1\c&H45444A&\frz22.88\move(233,154.5,224,153.5)}Favorite music!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs10\t(\fs11)\b1\an9\c&H45444A&\frz23.22\move(331,114,333,110)}Listens to only \Nthis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs8\t(\fs8.5)\b1\an8\c&H45444A&\frz23.22\move(318,142.5,317,140.5)}Borrows albums\Nfrom Ohmori
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs8\t(\fs8.5)\b1\an8\c&H45444A&\frz23.22\move(175.5,205.5,165.5,208.5)}Going to\Na concert\Nsoon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs8\t(\fs8.5)\b1\an8\c&H45444A&\frz23.22\move(338,167,339,166)}With Ohmori?!\NSo jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs12\t(\fs13)\b1\an1\c&H45444A&\frz23.22\move(279.5,220.5,277.5,222.5)}Aquapet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\u1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs10\t(\fs11)\b1\an1\c&H45444A&\move(215,306,206,316)\frz24.61}Smash Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:53.99,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs8\t(\fs9)\b1\an8\c&H45444A&\frz23.22\move(343.5,236,345.5,240)}Mobile game, \Ncurrently super popular\N{\fs10\t(\fs11)}Seriously? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:50.07,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I learned a lot about Hirose today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.96,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,There's so much I don't know about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:57.37,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Has cola always been this dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.62,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Maybe the color's different \Nbecause it's sugar-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:04.52,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,If you don't want it, \Nwhy don't you get a new one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.49,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Dude, gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.60,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,What? I-It was that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.13,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,What did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:22.99,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,I'm filming this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.02,Default,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Sorry. Do you want another?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.23,Default,TAKEUCHI,0,0,0,,Like hell I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.63,Default,STUDENT,0,0,0,,Bye, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:34.41,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,Bye. Take care on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:35.95,Default,STUDENTS,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:07.10,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,Oh, Niou-sensei. You're always running.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.84,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,Yes. To stay in shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.61,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:16.37,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.25,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:23.65,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,Oh, you noticed? Aren't they pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.50,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,They bloomed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:30.13,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,They're called cyclamen,\N and they bloom in the colder months.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:33.57,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,Niou-sensei, do you like flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.74,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,There are other pretty flowers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.54,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,I'll display them sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:39.91,Default,NIOU,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:42.78,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry for stopping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.82,Default,KOORI,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.05,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:54.42,Default,OTOGIRI,0,0,0,,We're still a long way from spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.28,Default,TAKU,0,0,0,,Hey, get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.91,Default,MAKU,0,0,0,,Why? We're in love, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:03.41,Default,TAKU,0,0,0,,That was something I just blurted out. \NI don't know what love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.16,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord1.2\an1\fscx0\t(30,600,\fscx135)\fscy2\shad3\fs34\t(\fs36)\blur3\4c&HE0C2D5&\3c&HD9B1E2&\p1\frz11.5\move(391,77,395,73)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100{\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.74,0:12:07.16,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\bord1.2\shad3\fs34\t(\fs36)\blur3\4c&HE0C2D5&\3c&HD9B1E2&\frz10.27\move(390,114,395,110)}This is the love story{\u0}\Nof two lunches
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:07.16,Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,This is the love story of two lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:13.45,Default,MAKU,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll show you \Nexactly what love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.30,Default,TAKU,0,0,0,,M-Makunouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.43,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an8\xshad-3\yshad4\bord1\b1\blur0.3\fs60\pos(504,11.5)\c&H0400C6&\3c&H120593&}A rival\Nappears
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.43,Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Then, a rival appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.06,Default,MAKU,0,0,0,,A-Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:33.46,Default,MAKU & TAKU,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:34.94,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fnGeorgia\b1\fs34\blur1\bord1.5\shad0\pos(320,254)\3c&HCD8EF6&\c&HCD8EF6&\t(100,500,\3c&HFCF2F5&\c&H0C0100&)}What will be the fate of their love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.94,Default,NARRATION,0,0,0,,What will be the fate of their love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.23,Default,TAKU,0,0,0,,Makunouchi! Makunouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.70,Default,TAKU,0,0,0,,Makunouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:42.70,Default,MAKU,0,0,0,,Taku! I'll be the one to microwave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.27,Default,MAKU,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone else microwave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.21,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\an8\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fs86\shad0\blur0.3\bord5\3c&HFEFBFB&\4c&H406591&\c&H3B1EDF&\pos(320,2)}Lov{\c&H069AF0&}able {\c&H3C21DC&}Lun{\c&H069AF0&}ch{\c&H3C21DC&}es{\c&H069AF0&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.21,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\fnGeorgia\b1\fs50\shad0\bord2.5\c&H3E1DE3&\3c&HFBFFFC&\pos(320,263)}Anime greenlit!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.29,Default,TAKU,0,0,0,,Lovable Lunches!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.21,Default,MAKU & TAKU,0,0,0,,Anime greenlit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:52.21,Default,MAKU,0,0,0,,If you get too warm, you'll explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.34,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an8\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fs22\shad0\blur0.3\bord2\3c&HF4F0FC&\4c&H406591&\c&H3B1EDF&\pos(318,70.5)}Lov{\c&H069AF0&}able {\c&H3C21DC&}Lun{\c&H069AF0&}ch{\c&H3C21DC&}es{\c&H069AF0&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.34,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\fnGeorgia\b1\fs13\shad0\bord1\c&H3E1DE3&\3c&HD3CEEC&\pos(317,136)}Anime greenlit!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:13:00.30,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fnComic Sans MS\b1\blur0.3\bord0.5\fs30\shad2\pos(440,315)\3c&H0E0E0E&\4c&H0E0E0E&}Super Exciting! \NLovable Lunches Autograph Signing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.55,Italics Top,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,The day has finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.68,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fs25\xshad2\blur0.3\bord1.5\3c&H24317D&\4c&H406591&\c&H3B99E9&\frz355.5\pos(160,130)}Lovable {\c&H60D3FA&}Lunches{\c&H2798F3&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:03.80,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I've been reading it\Never since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.43,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,No, since the series started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.68,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,My favorite storylines are, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:14.44,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,First, there's Makunouchi's confession \Nand the elusive special.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.86,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,There's also Taku's homemade juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.96,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Oh, and their awakening to new flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:23.45,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Ah, I could go on about it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.08,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,The day has finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:30.58,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I've been looking forward\N to this since forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.58,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fs35\xshad2\blur0.3\bord1.5\3c&H787A96&\4c&H888AA4&\c&H92C5F6&\pos(458,108)\frx35\fry8}Lovable {\c&H9BD9FB&}Lunches{\c&H92C5F6&}!
