Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.58,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Today's the {\i0}Lovable Lunches{\i1} anime \Ngreen-lighting autograph session!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.84,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,Hifumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.34,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,Have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.68,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry. Give me another minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.57,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Could I get this, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.13,Default,CLERK,0,0,0,,Is this for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.72,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,It's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:46.61,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:47.96,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,That took forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.55,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,Now, now. We have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.41,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,Let's get some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:55.24,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,In that case, there's somewhere\N I'd like to go. Is that okay?
