Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:53.82,Default,WAITRESS,0,0,0,,So one French toast sandwich, \None character lunch, and one love lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.41,Default,WAITRESS,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.11,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:58.09,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.42,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,You probably could've \Nshortened the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.35,Italics Top,TAKU,0,0,0,,Hey, get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.09,Italics Top,MAKU,0,0,0,,Why? We're in love, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:08.31,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Wow, they're really moving and talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:10.20,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,I'm glad you got a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.31,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,Yeah, you really love {\i1}Lovable Lunches{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:16.31,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,I'll finally get to see their awakening \Nto new flavors animated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:21.57,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming \Nall the way here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:24.24,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,It's fine. We wanted \Nto come to Animate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.45,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,By the way, did you finish \Nwriting your letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:31.20,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. It took all night \Nsince there was so much I wanted to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.45,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.53,Default,WAITRESS,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.65,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,This actually looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.76,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,The portions are big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.59,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:48.34,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,These are too cute to eat.
