Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:04.61,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I'll get to see their awakening \Nto new flavors animated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.49,Flashback,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Hey, get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:10.12,Flashback,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Why? We're in love, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:13.41,Flashback,HIROSE,0,0,0,,Th-That was something I just blurted out. \NI don't know what love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:17.87,Flashback,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll show you \Nexactly what love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.36,Flashback,HIROSE,0,0,0,,N-Nakamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:26.46,Default,FEMALE A,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me. \NI'd like to grab one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.15,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,S-S-S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.29,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Crap, crap, crap.
