Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:36.85,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,{\i0}Lovable Lunches{\i1}' Kometani Ii-sensei's\N autograph session.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.33,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd get a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.18,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,But somehow, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.05,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,My luck hasn't run out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:44.86,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\bord2\shad0\fs10\t(\fs11)\blur0.3\b1\fscx85\move(319,33,319,20)\c&H6138B3&\3c&HF6F6F6&}Lovable Lunches! Autograph Session Invitation\NCelebrating the Anime Green-Lighting & New Volume Release
