Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:44.86,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\bord2\shad0\fs11\t(\fs12.5)\blur0.3\fscx85\c&H6138B3&\3c&HF6F6F6&\move(377,131,382,126)}[Not For Resale or Transfer]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:44.86,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\bord2\shad0\fs13\t(\fs14)\blur0.3\fscx85\c&HF6F7F6&\3c&H5723B5&\move(321,150.5,321,148)}This ticket is required to receive an autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:44.86,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\bord2\shad0\fs13\t(\fs14)\blur0.3\fscx85\c&HF6F7F6&\3c&H5723B5&\move(322,161.5,322,160.5)}Do not forget to bring it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:44.86,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\bord2\shad0\fs8\t(\fs9)\blur0.3\fscx85\c&H6138B3&\3c&HF6F6F6&\move(312,184,314,185)}Only the ticket holder may attend the autograph session.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:44.86,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\bord2\shad0\fs8\t(\fs9)\blur0.3\fscx85\c&HF6F7F6&\3c&H5723B5&\move(299.5,210,297.5,212)}Animate Ikebukuro
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:44.86,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\bord2\shad0\fs8\t(\fs9)\blur0.3\fscx85\c&HF6F7F6&\3c&H5723B5&\move(298.5,228.5,296.5,232.5)}Main Store
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.72,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,{\i1}Detective Bari Kata{\i0} is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.61,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,I love the actor who plays the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.61,Top,YUUKA,0,0,0,,I didn't think they'd cast\N a Hollywood actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.61,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,K-Kawamura-san? What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.90,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:56.52,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,I thought I saw someone looking at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.93,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Maybe I imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:02.13,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,We're gonna check out the merch upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.38,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,I'll head up once I'm finished down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.24,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Kawamura-san's by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.50,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I should be able to hide until it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:21.44,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fnArial\bord2\shad0\fs9\blur0.3\b1\fscx75\fax0.4\c&H6138B3&\3c&HF6F6F6&\pos(318,96)}Lovable Lunches! Autograph Session Invitation\NCelebrating the Anime Green-Lighting & New Volume Release
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:21.44,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! She's going to \Nthe autograph session, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.41,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,What should I do? Leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:26.19,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,But I'm really looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.76,Top,EMPLOYEE A,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Lovable Lunches{\i0} autograph session\N will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:34.20,Top,EMPLOYEE A,0,0,0,,Ticket holders, please sign in and enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:30.54,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Crud. It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:34.20,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I'll have to use my ace in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.20,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\an9\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fs20\shad1.5\blur0.3\bord1.5\3c&H6D5D5E&\4c&H6B6163&\c&HC297F3&\pos(266.5,300.5)\frz312.9}Lov{\c&HEFD494&}able {\c&HC297F3&}Lun{\c&HEFD494&}ches{\c&H2798F3&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.87,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Yup, good. This'll do for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.83,Default,SECURITY,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.87,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:49.62,Default,SECURITY,0,0,0,,For security reasons, could you remove \Nthat cloth on your face before entering?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.23,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Oh, a-actually, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:54.35,Default,SECURITY,0,0,0,,May I see your ID as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:56.10,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,What? Actually, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.48,Top,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:02.11,Top,SECURITY,0,0,0,,I'll be the judge of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.48,Italics,KAWAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Wow, there are all kinds \Nof people in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.86,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD5AFF9&\fnComic Sans MS\pos(109.538,116.615)}Badump
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:02.85,Italics,KAWAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Huh? That slouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:06.50,Italics,KAWAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,And those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.43,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Nakamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:13.11,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Thanks. Sorry about that, Kawamura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:16.24,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,It's totally fine. \NI'm glad we were able to clear it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.29,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,It's even more embarrassing \Nsince she instantly knew it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.89,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Anyway, I never expected \Nto run into you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.50,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,You won a ticket, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:29.49,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I-I should come clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:30.51,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,I actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.76,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.61,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,I love {\i1}Lovable Lunches{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.76,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,What? Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.33,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,What? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:43.02,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,You read it at school sometimes, \Nso I figured you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:45.14,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Oh, she already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.89,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Sorry. Was that supposed to be a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:51.28,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,By the way, what's your favorite storyline?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:54.31,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,What? Well, it's hard to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:57.21,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,I like Makunouchi's confession...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.53,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Ah, that's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:03.04,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,But my favorite's probably Taku and \NMakunouchi's awakening to new flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:06.22,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Right? That's my favorite storyline, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.48,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.54,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:15.10,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,It's so good. It's like \Ntheir feelings become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:18.08,Default,EMPLOYEE A,0,0,0,,The autograph session will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:21.01,Default,EMPLOYEE A,0,0,0,,Please follow the instructions \Nof the staff and move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.46,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,I'd better get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:26.78,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:30.22,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,A letter. You don't get much time\N at these events,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:32.40,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,so I wrote down everything\N I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.28,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Th-That's a brilliant idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:37.54,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,It didn't occur to me to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.86,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Wh-What's in the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.83,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,A gift. I had trouble \Ndeciding what to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.92,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,That's another brilliant idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:50.51,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Oh, you're not required \Nto bring anything. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.59,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:52.88,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,550)\an9\fnArial Black\shad0\blur0.3\bord4\fax0.08\pos(469.5,62)\frz355.1\3c&HFFFEFF&\c&H4D86DE&}Kometani Ii-sensei\h\h\h\h{\3c&H6DA5F2&\bord0\c&HFDFFFE&}Autograph Session
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:54.60,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.22,Default,GUEST 1,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:58.47,Default,STAFF,0,0,0,,Next person, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.13,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,It's almost our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.22,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.10,Default,GUEST 2,0,0,0,,The new volume was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.54,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,Thanks. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:07.98,Default,GUEST 2,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.48,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,We get less time to talk than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.94,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I'll skip my thoughts on the special,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.75,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,and just talk about Makunouchi's \Nconfession and the new flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.61,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Oh, but I want to talk about Taku, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.52,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't narrow down what I want to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:29.08,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I should've written a letter like Kawamura-san,\N despite what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.75,Top,STAFF,0,0,0,,Next person, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.11,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,It's Kawamura-san's turn already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.50,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,I've been reading {\i1}Lovable Lunches{\i0}\N since it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.86,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,I have a letter and gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:40.16,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,Thanks. Which character would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.21,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Um, Makunouchi-kun, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:43.51,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,Makunouchi-kun? Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.05,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,What? We get a drawing of a character?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.56,Italics,NAKAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,Is that even allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:48.58,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.08,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.25,Default,STAFF,0,0,0,,Next person, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:55.78,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:10.42,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,I l-l-love {\i1}Lovable Lunches{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:16.66,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Uh, um... T-Taku-kun is really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:24.47,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'm glad to hear you say that,\N since I like Taku, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.09,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,Would you like a drawing of Taku-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.54,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.10,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,You're a student, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.31,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.73,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:35.06,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,Nakamura-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.29,Default,YONEUCHI,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:40.01,Default,NAKAMURA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.22,Default,STAFF,0,0,0,,Next person, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:44.10,Default,FAN A,0,0,0,,I'm a huge fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:48.57,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,What a haul. I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.38,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,You bought way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:52.92,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,If you want something, \Nyou have to jump on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:55.70,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,Parents and merch won't be around forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.28,Default,MASAKO,0,0,0,,How'd it go, Hifumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.17,Default,KAWAMURA,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:02.04,Default,YUUKA,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:07.43,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord5\shad0\fnGeorgia\fscx95\blur0.3\fs25\c&H4E5C64&\3c&HE2F0F5&\pos(196,14.5)}To Kawamura-san!\NKometani Ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:06.74,Italics,KAWAMURA/ID,0,0,0,,I'm glad I got to attend the event \Nwith Nakamura-kun.
